mia and roman is a 1968 &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; documentary film which was shot during the making of rosemary 's baby . the title refers to mia farrow and roman polanski . the film features footage of roman polanski directing the film 's cast on set . it was directed by &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; hatami . it was screened as a promo film at hollywood 's lytton center , and later included as a featurette on the dvd of rosemary 's baby . it is described as a " &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; on-set featurette " and " an odd little bit of cheese " .